      "content": "i get that youre supposed to say a doctor, but i'm looking for more info. like, strictly from a chemistry standpoint, if i only take a small amount of the supplement once a day, is the risk of serotonin syndrome actually that high? or is it more of a theoretical thing that rarely happens in real life?",
